2026-05-16T23:53:58.0887380Z 26            MainActivity when canScheduleExactAlarms() returns false.
2026-05-16T23:53:58.0887708Z 27          - USE_EXACT_ALARM: auto-granted on Android 13+ (API 33+) for
2026-05-16T23:53:58.0888046Z 28            calendar/reminder/timer-style apps, so no prompt is needed.
2026-05-16T23:53:58.0888386Z 29        Without USE_EXACT_ALARM the app was silently falling back to
